He was appointed Under-Secretary of the Synod of Bishops on 8 February 2014 by Pope Francis, Giovanni Battista Cardinal Re and Lorenzo Cardinal Baldisseri.

He was elevated to the episcopate by Francis as [[Titular Bishop]] of Aquipendium on 8 April and was consecrated on 30 May 2014.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bfabene.html Bishop Fabio Fabene]</ref>

===Other===
Fabene serves as the postulator in the cause of canonization of the late [[Venerable]] [[Cardinal (Catholicism)|Cardinal]] Marcantonio Barbarigo (1640-1706).

